OL,3,C'This is getting spicy': NI man in UAE
OL,4,Cwitnesses rockets explode in sky
OL,6,FBy Nathan Hylands
OL,8,FA Northern Ireland man who is a
OL,9,Fresident in The United Arab Emirates
OL,10,Fhas said missile interceptions
OL,11,F"vibrate the whole place".
OL,13,FJoe Girvin from Dungannon, was living
OL,14,Fin Dubai with his fiancee Xanthe Hay
OL,15,Fbefore strikes carried out by Israel
OL,16,Fand the US killed Iran's Supreme
OL,17,FLeader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei.
OL,26,@vD@Xrr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
