OL,3,C'This is getting spicy': NI man in UAE
OL,4,Cwitnesses rockets explode in sky
OL,6,FThere have been missile and drone
OL,7,Fattacks in multiple Gulf states after
OL,8,FIran vowed to carry out its "most
OL,9,Fintense operation" ever in retaliation.
OL,11,FThe musician was performing at a gig
OL,12,Fon Saturday afternoon when the attacks
OL,13,Fbegan.
OL,15,F"We didn't know any of this was gonna
OL,16,Fhappen, it just started," he told UTV.
OL,18,F"There was explosions in the air from
OL,19,Fabout 3pm. I heard them from a
OL,20,Fdistance over the city and then they
OL,21,Fwere right above my head.
OL,26,@pD@]OUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772571963
OL,3,C'This is getting spicy': NI man in UAE
OL,4,Cwitnesses rockets explode in sky
OL,6,F"One missile was intercepted right
OL,7,Fabove us and I was like, 'this is
OL,8,Fgetting spicy'.
OL,10,F"We were told to stay indoors but I
OL,11,Fwas still gigging until 9pm and by
OL,12,Fthat time it was dark.
OL,14,F"I saw like four orange lights fly
OL,15,Finto the sky and I was like 'oh God,
OL,16,Fthese are right above us again'.
OL,18,F"They had intercepted another three or
OL,19,Ffour from a distance above us. Then
OL,20,Fthe venue decided to close and
OL,21,Feveryone was like 'let's get home'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
