PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772571963
OL,3,C'This is getting spicy': NI man in UAE
OL,4,Cwitnesses rockets explode in sky
OL,6,F"I think we saw about 18 or 20 in the
OL,7,Ffirst day. They are like really loud
OL,8,Fbangs, which vibrate like a shutter,
OL,9,Fit vibrates the whole place.
OL,11,F"On Sunday, they were a lot louder and
OL,12,Fthey shook everything around us," he
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,FThe pair moved alongside their seven
OL,16,Fpets from Dubai to the city of Ras Al
OL,17,FKhaimah around 70 miles away.
OL,19,F"We uprooted from Dubai and then came
OL,20,Fdown to my fiancee's mum's house.
OL,26,@|D@Qrr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
