PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772571963
OL,3,C'This is getting spicy': NI man in UAE
OL,4,Cwitnesses rockets explode in sky
OL,6,F"We are lucky enough she lives here
OL,7,Ftoo," Mr Girvin said.
OL,9,F"All we hear now is fighter jets.
OL,10,FThere has been explosions and debris
OL,11,Fdid hit near this place this morning,
OL,12,Fabout 10 minutes away from us.
OL,14,F"The officials have just said stay
OL,15,Findoors, don't go out if you don't
OL,16,Fhave to, stay away from windows and
OL,17,Fglass.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
