PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772571963
OL,3,C'This is getting spicy': NI man in UAE
OL,4,Cwitnesses rockets explode in sky
OL,6,F"They said there is loud sounds, this
OL,7,Fis going to happen for the next while
OL,8,Funtil this stops, but you are as safe
OL,9,Fas possible because of the defence
OL,10,Fsystems over the Middle East.
OL,12,F"The first twelve hours, that was
OL,13,Fscary. It was just us sitting there
OL,14,Fgoing like 'if stuff starts blowing up
OL,15,Fin front of us, what are we going to
OL,16,Fdo?'.
OL,18,F"I feel a lot calmer now but there's
OL,19,Fno time frame how long is this going
OL,20,Fto go on for.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
