PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772571963
OL,3,C'This is getting spicy': NI man in UAE
OL,4,Cwitnesses rockets explode in sky
OL,6,F"They still have bars and restaurants
OL,7,Fopen. They're trying to maintain
OL,8,Feverything as normal as possible."
OL,10,FAirspace closures in the Middle East
OL,11,Fhave resulted in a number of
OL,12,Fcommercial flights being grounded
OL,13,Fsince the attacks began.
OL,15,F"If it gets worse, I would definitely
OL,16,Fgo home, but obviously there's a lot
OL,17,Fof people stuck in the airports now.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
