PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772571963
OL,3,C'This is getting spicy': NI man in UAE
OL,4,Cwitnesses rockets explode in sky
OL,6,F"There was no warning because I know
OL,7,Fthat I was talking to my ones at home
OL,8,Fand they're like, 'oh this has been
OL,9,Fbuilding up for weeks', and we were
OL,10,Flike, 'what do you mean?'
OL,12,F"You just stay as calm as possible,
OL,13,Fbecause we can't control what's
OL,14,Fhappening.
OL,16,F"I've got texts from home since this
OL,17,Fstarted just asking, 'are you safe and
OL,18,Fwhat's happening?'"
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
