OL,3,C'This is getting spicy': NI man in UAE
OL,4,Cwitnesses rockets explode in sky
OL,6,FBritish nationals are being advised to
OL,7,Ffollow the instructions of local
OL,8,Fauthorities and monitor the Foreign
OL,9,FOffice's travel advice, which
OL,10,Fofficials expect to change rapidly.
OL,12,FThose in Bahrain, Israel, Kuwait,
OL,13,FPalestine, Qatar and the United Arab
OL,14,FEmirates (UAE) have been urged to
OL,15,Fregister their presence with the
OL,16,FForeign Office online.
OL,18,FIrish citizens in the Middle East have
OL,19,Fbeen urged to adopt a "shelter in
OL,20,Fplace" strategy by Ireland's Foreign
OL,21,FAffairs Minister.
OL,26,@{D@WOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
